        <Parent_String>Colonial Latin American fine arts styles [300107840], Colonial Latin American styles [300018082], Latin American [300080819], The Americas [300016617], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
